714851f-a.title: Manhattan: 94th Street (East) - 2nd Avenue
714851f-a.text:
308 and 310 East 94th Street, south side, east of Second Ave. Upon
the excavation at the right was constructed a 2-story garage (No. 304-306).
April 21, 1917.
Underwood \& Underwood.
